I believe that your discussion would be easier to follow for those in 
this group if you used the names given the letters as opposed to using 
the numbers.  I don&#39;t carry the QS alphabet around with me on a sheet of 
paper and I suspect most of us don&#39;t.  I never learned the letters by 
numbers.  I suppose we could refer to &quot;m&quot; as &quot;#13,&quot; but most people 
don&#39;t do so.

Just an suggestion.

Regards,

Paige


